data.description: This beautifully maintained newer 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom Norris manufactured home is located in a very nice 55+ community with low HOA fees. This one level home is at the end of a cul-de-sac with a large fenced in back yard. The open floor plan makes the home feel very roomy and the sheet rock walls throughout the home are a very nice upgrade. The primary bedroom is spacious and the primary bath includes a tub and shower. The kitchen is equipped with tons of storage space and nice appliances. The attached carport has room to park two vehicles and there is also additional room to park in the driveway. This home is conveniently only a short drive to downtown Hendersonville, shopping and restaurants. Schedule your showing today!
